<h2><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~ics54/">ICS 54</A>:
Brief Notes on Encryption and Security
</h2>

<b>The Greatest Threat to Network Security is Human Care-less-ness.</b>

<h3>Functions of Encryption</h3>
<ul>
  <li><b>C</b>onfidentiality
  <li><b>A</b>uthentication
  <li><b>I</b>ntegrity
  <li><b>N</b>onrepudiation
</ul>
<p>

